<feed xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>Ortaya Karƒ±≈üƒ±k - Laravel Geli≈ütirme</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/" rel="alternate"/><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/feeds/laravel-gelistirme.atom.xml" rel="self"/><id>https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/</id><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><entry><title>Laravel IDE Helper Kullanƒ±mƒ±</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/laravel-ide-helper-kullanimi/" rel="alternate"/><published>2020-07-03T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.github.io,2020-07-03:/laravel-ide-helper-kullanimi/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Laravel IDE Helper paketi ile PHPStorm'da otomatik tamamlama ve kod yardƒ±mcƒ±sƒ± nasƒ±l geli≈ütirilir?&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h2 id="laravel-ide-helper-nedir"&gt;Laravel IDE Helper Nedir? üöÄ&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bir &lt;strong&gt;IDE (Entegre Geli&amp;scedil;tirme Ortam&amp;inodot;)&lt;/strong&gt;, yaz&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;m geli&amp;scedil;tirme s&amp;uuml;recini kolayla&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;ran ve bir&amp;ccedil;ok geli&amp;scedil;tirme arac&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; bir araya getiren yaz&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;md&amp;inodot;r. Pop&amp;uuml;ler IDE'ler aras&amp;inodot;nda Eclipse, Microsoft Visual Studio, Code Blocks, Dev-C++, NetBeans ve JetBrains &amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;nleri bulunur.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Laravel projeleri geli&amp;scedil;tirirken &lt;strong&gt;PHPStorm&lt;/strong&gt; s&amp;inodot;k&amp;ccedil;a tercih edilen bir IDE'dir. Ancak, &lt;strong&gt;PHPStorm&lt;/strong&gt; baz&amp;inodot; model, class ve route bilgilerini otomatik olarak alg&amp;inodot;layamayabilir. Bu noktada, &lt;strong&gt;Laravel IDE Helper&lt;/strong&gt; paketi devreye girerek geli&amp;scedil;tirme deneyimini iyile&amp;scedil;tirir.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E&amp;gbreve;er bu paket olmasayd&amp;inodot;, &lt;strong&gt;PHPDoc&lt;/strong&gt; kullanarak bu bilgileri elle eklemek gerekecekti. Konu hakk&amp;inodot;nda daha fazla bilgi almak i&amp;ccedil;in &lt;strong&gt;Abdulkadir D&amp;inodot;lo S&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;c&amp;uuml;&lt;/strong&gt;'n&amp;uuml;n a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;klamalar&amp;inodot;na &amp;scedil;uradan ula&amp;scedil;abilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@justinribeiro/lite-youtube@1/lite-youtube.min.js" type="module"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;lite-youtube videoid="0NZHzmAgH-M"&gt;&lt;/lite-youtube&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="laravel-ide-helper-nasil-kurulur"&gt;Laravel IDE Helper Nas&amp;inodot;l Kurulur? üõ†Ô∏è&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Laravel projelerinde &lt;strong&gt;Laravel IDE Helper&lt;/strong&gt; paketini kurmak i&amp;ccedil;in a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki ad&amp;inodot;mlar&amp;inodot; takip edebilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id="1-paketi-kurun"&gt;1. Paketi Kurun&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Terminal veya komut sat&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;zda a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutu &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;composer&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;require&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;--dev&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;barryvdh/laravel-ide-helper
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="2-kod-tamamlamayi-etkinlestirin"&gt;2. Kod Tamamlamay&amp;inodot; Etkinle&amp;scedil;tirin&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutu &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;rarak proje dizininize &lt;strong&gt;_ide_helper.php&lt;/strong&gt; dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; olu&amp;scedil;turabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;php&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;artisan&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;ide-helper:generate
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="3-konfigurasyon-dosyasini-yayimlayin"&gt;3. Konfig&amp;uuml;rasyon Dosyas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; Yay&amp;inodot;mlay&amp;inodot;n&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Konfig&amp;uuml;rasyonu yay&amp;inodot;nlamak i&amp;ccedil;in a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutu kullanabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;php&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;artisan&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;vendor:publish&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;--provider&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"Barryvdh\LaravelIdeHelper\IdeHelperServiceProvider"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;--tag&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;config
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="4-modeller-icin-dokumantasyon-olusturun"&gt;4. Modeller &amp;Idot;&amp;ccedil;in Dok&amp;uuml;mantasyon Olu&amp;scedil;turun üìå&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baz&amp;inodot; modellerde &lt;strong&gt;"fonksiyon bulunamad&amp;inodot;"&lt;/strong&gt; uyar&amp;inodot;s&amp;inodot; ile kar&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;la&amp;scedil;abilirsiniz. Bunu &amp;ccedil;&amp;ouml;zmek i&amp;ccedil;in a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutu kullanabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;php&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;artisan&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;ide-helper:models&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;User
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;E&amp;gbreve;er model dosyalar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z farkl&amp;inodot; bir klas&amp;ouml;rdeyse, tam yolu belirtmelisiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;php&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;artisan&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;ide-helper:models&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Model&lt;span class="se"&gt;\U&lt;/span&gt;ser
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu i&amp;scedil;lemin sonunda, &lt;strong&gt;User.php&lt;/strong&gt; gibi model dosyalar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;n ba&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;nda &amp;scedil;u &amp;scedil;ekilde bir PHPDoc blok olu&amp;scedil;turulur:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;PHP&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="x"&gt;/**&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * App\User&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; *&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * @property int $id&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * @property string $name&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * @property string $email&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * @property \Illuminate\Support\Carbon|null $created_at&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * @property \Illuminate\Support\Carbon|null $updated_at&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; * @mixin \Eloquent&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="x"&gt; */&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 id="5-composera-otomatik-komutlar-ekleyin"&gt;5. Composer'a Otomatik Komutlar Ekleyin üîÑ&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;composer.json&lt;/code&gt; dosyan&amp;inodot;za a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki scriptleri ekleyerek, &lt;strong&gt;composer update&lt;/strong&gt; komutu &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;ld&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;nda dok&amp;uuml;mantasyon dosyalar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;n otomatik olarak g&amp;uuml;ncellenmesini sa&amp;gbreve;layabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;JSON&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;"scripts"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nt"&gt;"post-update-cmd"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"Illuminate\\Foundation\\ComposerScripts::postUpdate"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"@php artisan ide-helper:generate"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"@php artisan ide-helper:meta"&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="w"&gt;    &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="p"&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="sonuc_1"&gt;Sonu&amp;ccedil; üéØ&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Laravel IDE Helper&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;PHPStorm&lt;/strong&gt; gibi IDE'lerde kod tamamlama ve otomatik &amp;ouml;nerileri iyile&amp;scedil;tirerek geli&amp;scedil;tirme deneyimini &amp;ccedil;ok daha verimli hale getirir. Daha fazla bilgi i&amp;ccedil;in &lt;a href="https://github.com/barryvdh/laravel-ide-helper/blob/master/README.md" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Laravel IDE Helper Wiki&lt;/a&gt; sayfas&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; ziyaret edebilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PhpStorm ile ilgili daha fazla yaz&amp;inodot;ya &lt;a href="/etiket/phpstorm/"&gt;buradan ula&amp;scedil;abilirsiniz&lt;/a&gt;. üöÄ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Laravel IDE Helper" class="responsive-img" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, (max-width: 992px) 80vw, (max-width: 1400px) 70vw, 60vw" src="/images/laravel_7x_ide_helper-xl.webp" srcset="/images/laravel_7x_ide_helper-sm.webp 300w, /images/laravel_7x_ide_helper-md.webp 500w, /images/laravel_7x_ide_helper-xl.webp 800w, /images/laravel_7x_ide_helper-xl.webp 1200w"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Laravel Geli≈ütirme"/><category term="phpstorm"/><category term="cmder"/></entry><entry><title>Arch Linux Laravel Valet Kurulumu</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/arch-linux-laravel-valet-kurulumu/" rel="alternate"/><published>2020-06-15T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.github.io,2020-06-15:/arch-linux-laravel-valet-kurulumu/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Valet Linux, minimalist geli≈ütirme ortamƒ±nƒ± sevenler i√ßin ideal bir Laravel geli≈ütirme ortamƒ±dƒ±r. Vagrant veya /etc/hosts ayarlamaya gerek kalmadan, yerel t√ºnelleri kullanarak sitelerinizi kolayca payla≈üabilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h1 id="merhaba"&gt;Merhaba üëã&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Valet Linux, minimalist bir geli&amp;scedil;tirme ortam&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; tercih edenler i&amp;ccedil;in Laravel geli&amp;scedil;tirme ortam&amp;inodot;d&amp;inodot;r. &lt;a href="/archlinux-virtualbox-vagrant-laravel-phpmyadmin-kurulumu" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Vagrant&lt;/a&gt; veya &lt;code&gt;/etc/hosts&lt;/code&gt; ayarlamaya gerek yoktur. Yerel t&amp;uuml;nelleri (Ngrok vb.) kullanarak sitelerinizi herkese a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k olarak payla&amp;scedil;abilirsiniz. üöÄ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Valet, sisteminizi makine a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;ld&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;nda &lt;strong&gt;Nginx'i arka planda &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;racak &amp;scedil;ekilde yap&amp;inodot;land&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;r&lt;/strong&gt;. Ard&amp;inodot;ndan, &lt;strong&gt;DnsMasq&lt;/strong&gt; kullanarak &lt;code&gt;*.test&lt;/code&gt; uzant&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot; domainlerinizi ilgili dizinlere y&amp;ouml;nlendirir. &lt;strong&gt;Sadece 7MB RAM kullanarak &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;an, h&amp;inodot;zl&amp;inodot; ve hafif bir Laravel geli&amp;scedil;tirme ortam&amp;inodot; sunar.&lt;/strong&gt; üéØ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="info-box warning"&gt;
&lt;svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewbox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;
&lt;path d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div class="alert-title"&gt;&amp;Ouml;nceki Kurulumlar&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Daha &amp;ouml;nce &lt;a href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/arch-linux-lampp-kurulumu-php7x-mariadb-mysql-phpmyadmin/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank"&gt;Arch Linux Lampp Kurulumu (PHP7x + MariaDB + MySQL + PhpMyAdmin)&lt;/a&gt; veya benzeri kurulumlar yapt&amp;inodot;ysan&amp;inodot;z, devre d&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot; b&amp;inodot;rakmal&amp;inodot; ya da kald&amp;inodot;rmal&amp;inodot;s&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z. Aksi takdirde &amp;ccedil;ak&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;malar ya&amp;scedil;anabilir.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="kurulum"&gt;üõ† Kurulum&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Terminali a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;n ve a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutlar&amp;inodot; s&amp;inodot;ras&amp;inodot;yla &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot;n:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;pacman&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;nss&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;jq&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;xsel&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;networkmanager
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PHP'nin kurulu ve 5.6'dan y&amp;uuml;ksek bir s&amp;uuml;r&amp;uuml;m oldu&amp;gbreve;undan emin olun:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;pacman&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="c1"&gt;# Kurulum sonras&amp;inodot; kontrol i&amp;ccedil;in: php -v&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Gerekli ek PHP paketlerini y&amp;uuml;kleyin:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;yay&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php71-mcrypt
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Idot;ste&amp;gbreve;e ba&amp;gbreve;l&amp;inodot; paketler:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;yay&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php-dblib&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php-fpm&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php-gd&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php-odbc&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php-pgsql&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;php-sqlite
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Composer kurun:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;yay&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;composer
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Daha sonra &lt;code&gt;.bashrc&lt;/code&gt; i&amp;ccedil;erisine &amp;scedil;u sat&amp;inodot;r&amp;inodot; ekleyin:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$HOME&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;/.config/composer/vendor/bin:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$PATH&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;"&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Composer'&amp;inodot; haz&amp;inodot;r hale getirin ve Valet Linux'u y&amp;uuml;kleyin:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;composer&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;global&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;require&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;cpriego/valet-linux
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h2 id="valet-ile-calisma"&gt;üéâ Valet ile &amp;Ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;ma&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ana dizine gidip &lt;code&gt;Sites&lt;/code&gt; ad&amp;inodot;nda bir klas&amp;ouml;r olu&amp;scedil;turun:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;mkdir&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;~/Sites
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bu klas&amp;ouml;r i&amp;ccedil;inde her alt klas&amp;ouml;r bir domain ad&amp;inodot; gibi &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;acakt&amp;inodot;r. &amp;Ouml;rne&amp;gbreve;in, &lt;code&gt;blog&lt;/code&gt; isimli bir Laravel projesi olu&amp;scedil;turup park edelim:&lt;/p&gt;
