&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt="Laravel Valet Kurulumu" class="responsive-img" loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 576px) 100vw, (max-width: 992px) 80vw, (max-width: 1400px) 70vw, 60vw" src="/images/laravel-valet-kurulumu-linux-xl.webp" srcset="/images/laravel-valet-kurulumu-linux-sm.webp 300w, /images/laravel-valet-kurulumu-linux-md.webp 500w, /images/laravel-valet-kurulumu-linux-xl.webp 800w, /images/laravel-valet-kurulumu-linux-xl.webp 1200w"/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content><category term="Laravel Geli≈ütirme"/><category term="linux"/><category term="laravel"/></entry><entry><title>Arch Linux √úzerinde VirtualBox + Vagrant + Laravel + PhpMyAdmin Kurulumu (Homestead)</title><link href="https://yuceltoluyag.github.io/archlinux-virtualbox-vagrant-laravel-phpmyadmin-kurulumu/" rel="alternate"/><published>2019-09-16T10:00:00+03:00</published><updated>2025-08-11T22:59:00+03:00</updated><author><name>yuceltoluyag</name></author><id>tag:yuceltoluyag.github.io,2019-09-16:/archlinux-virtualbox-vagrant-laravel-phpmyadmin-kurulumu/</id><summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;Arch Linux √ºzerinde VirtualBox, Vagrant, Laravel ve PhpMyAdmin kurulumunu adƒ±m adƒ±m anlatan detaylƒ± rehber.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><content type="html">&lt;h2 id="virtualbox-kurulumu"&gt;VirtualBox Kurulumu üöÄ&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;Ouml;ncelikle VirtualBox'&amp;inodot; y&amp;uuml;kleyelim:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;pacman&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-S&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;virtualbox
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kurulum s&amp;inodot;ras&amp;inodot;nda a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki se&amp;ccedil;enekler kar&amp;scedil;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;za &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;kacakt&amp;inodot;r:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;virtualbox-host-dkms&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;virtualbox-host-modules-arch&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hangi se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;i kullanaca&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; bilmiyorsan&amp;inodot;z:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;E&amp;gbreve;er &lt;strong&gt;Linux kerneli&lt;/strong&gt; kullan&amp;inodot;yorsan&amp;inodot;z &lt;strong&gt;2. se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;i&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;strong&gt;virtualbox-host-modules-arch&lt;/strong&gt;) se&amp;ccedil;melisiniz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Farkl&amp;inodot; bir kernel&lt;/strong&gt; kullan&amp;inodot;yorsan&amp;inodot;z &lt;strong&gt;1. se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;i&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;strong&gt;virtualbox-host-dkms&lt;/strong&gt;) tercih etmelisiniz.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ben &lt;strong&gt;2. se&amp;ccedil;ene&amp;gbreve;i&lt;/strong&gt; se&amp;ccedil;erek devam ediyorum.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kurulum tamamland&amp;inodot;ktan sonra VirtualBox'&amp;inodot; ba&amp;scedil;latmadan &amp;ouml;nce mod&amp;uuml;l&amp;uuml; etkinle&amp;scedil;tirelim:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;modprobe&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;vboxdrv
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;VirtualBox'&amp;inodot; bir kez &amp;ccedil;al&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;t&amp;inodot;rarak &lt;strong&gt;hata olup olmad&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; kontrol edin&lt;/strong&gt;. E&amp;gbreve;er hata al&amp;inodot;rsan&amp;inodot;z, hata mesaj&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; payla&amp;scedil;arak destek alabilirsiniz.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mod&amp;uuml;l&amp;uuml;n her a&amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;l&amp;inodot;&amp;scedil;ta otomatik y&amp;uuml;klenmesi i&amp;ccedil;in:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;nano&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;/etc/modules-load.d/virtualbox.conf
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dosyaya &lt;strong&gt;vboxdrv&lt;/strong&gt; ekleyin ve kaydedip &amp;ccedil;&amp;inodot;k&amp;inodot;n (&lt;strong&gt;F3&lt;/strong&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;strong&gt;Enter&lt;/strong&gt; -&amp;gt; &lt;strong&gt;F2&lt;/strong&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Son olarak, kullan&amp;inodot;c&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; &lt;strong&gt;vboxusers&lt;/strong&gt; grubuna ekleyin:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;usermod&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;-aG&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;vboxusers&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;KULLANICI_ADINIZ
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bilgisayar&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot;z&amp;inodot; yeniden ba&amp;scedil;latt&amp;inodot;ktan sonra a&amp;scedil;a&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;daki komutla mod&amp;uuml;l&amp;uuml;n y&amp;uuml;kl&amp;uuml; olup olmad&amp;inodot;&amp;gbreve;&amp;inodot;n&amp;inodot; do&amp;gbreve;rulayabilirsiniz:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;span class="filename"&gt;Bash&lt;/span&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;code&gt;sudo&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;lsmod&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="p"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;grep&lt;span class="w"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;vboxdrv
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
